headline: Booking.com Launches Credit Card That Makes It Easier to Earn and Use Rewards for Travel
summary: With a mission to make it easier for everyone to experience the world, Booking.com announces the launch of the Booking.com Genius Rewards Visa Signature® Credit Card, powered by Imprint, a leading platform for modern co-brand credit cards.
